title: Radio Free Asia Khamkay Webcast 18 December 2013
description:
ཨེ་ཤེ་ཡ་རང་དབང་རླུང་འཕྲིན་ཁང་གི་དྲ་བརྙན་གསར་འགྱུར།
Radio Free Asia Webcast Wednesday December 18, 2013.  We are delighted to announce that we are Webcasting in Amdo, Kham and U-Tsang dialects.   We would like our viewers to give comments or suggestions so we can continue to improve our programs. Thank you.
